snippet: Venus Williams defeated a qualifier, Iveta Benesova, 6-4, 6-3, in the Family Circle Cup in Charleston, S.C., her second tournament after a long layoff.
abstract: Venus Williams defeats Iveta Benesova in Family Circle Cup, her second tennis tournament after long layoff.
